# Environment Variables untuk Google Authentication

## Required Environment Variables

Tambahkan variabel environment berikut di Netlify Dashboard:

1. `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` - Client ID dari Google Cloud Console
2. `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` - Client Secret dari Google Cloud Console
3. `GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI` - URI redirect OAuth (contoh: https://rtcrypto.netlify.app/.netlify/functions/auth-callback)

## Langkah-langkah Setup Google OAuth:

1. Buka [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/)
2. Buat project baru atau pilih project yang sudah ada
3. Aktifkan Google+ API
4. Buka "Credentials" > "Create Credentials" > "OAuth 2.0 Client ID"
5. Pilih "Web application"
6. Tambahkan Authorized redirect URIs:
   - `https://rtcrypto.netlify.app/.netlify/functions/auth-callback`
   - `http://localhost:8888/.netlify/functions/auth-callback` (untuk development)
7. Copy Client ID dan Client Secret
8. Tambahkan ke Netlify Environment Variables di dashboard

## Set Environment Variables di Netlify:

1. Buka Netlify Dashboard
2. Pilih site "rtcrypto"
3. Pergi ke "Site configuration" > "Environment variables"
4. Tambahkan ketiga variabel di atas
5. Deploy ulang site
